phone Warehouse dropped Linux-based netbooks after seeing return rates as high as 20%.'' |title=Microsoft: 96% Of Netbooks Run Windows - Gains in PC market's hottest category come at the expense of Linux, Redmond says. |first=Paul |last=McDougall |publisher=InformationWeek |date=2009-04-06 |accessdate=2013-10-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012064500/http://www.informationweek.com/windows/operating-systems/microsoft-96-of-netbooks-run-windows/216402927 |archivedate=2013-10-12 }}</ref><ref>[http://blog.laptopmag.com/ubuntu-confirms-linux-netbook-returns-higher-than-anticpated Ubuntu Confirms Linux Netbook Returns Higher than Anticipated] {{Wayback|url=http://blog.laptopmag.com/ubuntu-confirms-linux-netbook-returns-higher-than-anticpated |date=20150712193841 }} on Laptopmag.com (Joanna Stern, 6 Oct 2008)</ref>

===行動裝置===
[[File:Android_Pie.png|thumb]]是根基於Linux的作業系統，在[[智能手機|智能手機]]上相當熱門。]]
Linux在行動裝置上最知名的應用莫過於[[Android|Android]]作業系統。Android發展自Linux，並且開放原始碼，目前是全世界市佔率最高的行動平台，全世界在2013年的第三季售出的[[智慧型手機|智慧型手機]]，有79.3%搭載了Android。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://techcrunch.com/2013/08/07/android-nears-80-market-share-in-global-smartphone-shipments-as-ios-and-blackberry-share-slides-per-idc/ | title = Android Nears 80% Market Share In Global Smartphone Shipments, As iOS And BlackBerry Share Slides, Per IDC | accessdate = 2014-08-03 | archive-date = 2021-02-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210201195039/https://techcrunch.com/2013/08/07/android-nears-80-market-share-in-global-smartphone-shipments-as-ios-and-blackberry-share-slides-per-idc/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>Android亦廣泛使用於[[平板電腦|平板電腦]]、[[智慧型手錶|智慧型手錶]]等裝置上。

