*在2007年，[[Google|Google]]推出了基於Linux核心的[[Android|Android]]作業系統，主要用於[[智慧型手機|智慧型手機]]和[[平板電腦|平板電腦]]。在2013年後半，Android在全世界的智慧型手機市場上達到80%的佔有率，<ref name="CNET Android statistic">{{cite news|title=Android dominates 81 percent of world smartphone market|url=http://news.cnet.com/8301-1035_3-57612057-94/android-dominates-81-percent-of-world-smartphone-market/|accessdate=3 January 2014|newspaper=CNET|date=November 12, 2013|archive-date=2014-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140209070330/http://news.cnet.com/8301-1035_3-57612057-94/android-dominates-81-percent-of-world-smartphone-market/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在平板電腦上則有60%的佔有率。<ref name="Tablet market share by operating system">{{cite news|title=IDC estimates 221m tablets shipped in 2013; Android top with 61%, then iOS 35% and Windows 3%|url=http://thenextweb.com/mobile/2013/12/04/idc-estimates-221m-tablets-shipped-in-2013-android-top-with-61-then-ios-35-and-windows-3/#!rfaV5|accessdate=3 January 2014|newspaper=The Next Web|date=4 December 2013|archive-date=2015-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208163300/http://thenextweb.com/mobile/2013/12/04/idc-estimates-221m-tablets-shipped-in-2013-android-top-with-61-then-ios-35-and-windows-3/#!rfaV5|dead-url=no}}</ref>
*在2011年，Google的[[Chromebook|Chromebook]]筆記型電腦問世，它的作業系統[[Chrome_OS|Chrome OS]]乃是基於[[Linux核心|Linux核心]]。在2013年，桌上型的Chromebox推出。在2013年Chromebooks在美國三百元以下的筆記型電腦市場中，有20~25%的佔有率。<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/google/10173494/Google-Chromebook-sales-soar-in-face-of-PC-decline.html|title = Google Chromebook sales soar in face of PC decline|date = 11 July 2013|accessdate = 3 September 2013|website = [[Daily_Telegraph|Daily Telegraph]]|last = Williams|first = Rhiannon|archive-date = 2019-04-20|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190420115434/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/google/10173494/Google-Chromebook-sales-soar-in-face-of-PC-decline.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>
*在2013年[[維爾福公司|維爾福公司]]發佈了Linux版的[[Steam|Steam]]和[[Source引擎|Source引擎]]，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://store.steampowered.com/news/9943/|title=News – Steam for Linux Now Available|accessdate=2014-08-03|archive-date=2019-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190529001345/https://store.steampowered.com/news/9943/|dead-url=no}}</ref>使該公司著名的電腦遊戲如[[絕地要塞2|絕地要塞2]]和[[戰慄時空2|戰慄時空2]]可以在Linux上執行。同年，維爾福宣佈正在開發[[遊戲主機|遊戲主機]][[Steam_Machine|Steam Machine]]，<ref>{{cite web |url= http://uk.gamespot.com/news/valve-reveals-steam-machines-6414959 |title= Valve reveals Steam Machines |date= 25 September 2013 |accessdate= 30 September 2013 |first= Eddie |last= Makuch |work= [[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130930035955/http://uk.gamespot.com/news/valve-reveals-steam-machines-6414959 |archivedate= 2013年9月30日 }}</ref>它的作業系統[[SteamOS|SteamOS]]將基於Linux核心。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-24207129 |title= Valve announces SteamOS as it renews living room push |date= 23 September 2013 |accessdate= 28 September 2013 |first= Dave |last= Lee |work= [[BBC|BBC]] |archive-date= 2020-12-31 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201231053802/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-24207129 |dead-url= no }}</ref>

===商業或非營利機構===
