*[[維基百科|維基百科]]的伺服器在2008年後半開始使用Ubuntu當作作業系統，而在這之前的作業系統是[[Red_Hat|Red Hat]]和[[Fedora|Fedora]]，這些都是Linux的發行版。<ref name="Paul09Oct08">{{cite web|url = http://arstechnica.com/open-source/news/2008/10/wikipedia-adopts-ubuntu-for-its-server-infrastructure.ars|title = Wikipedia adopts Ubuntu for its server infrastructure|accessdate = 2009-03-12|last = Paul|first = Ryan|authorlink = |date = October 2008|archive-date = 2011-02-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110223102711/http://arstechnica.com/open-source/news/2008/10/wikipedia-adopts-ubuntu-for-its-server-infrastructure.ars|dead-url = no}}</ref>
